{
  "id": "adv_card_ktn_07_02",
  "title": "長瀬琴乃 2話 奇抜過ぎる乗り方",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、ありがとうございます\n練習に付き合ってくれて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚  {user}-san.\nFor helping me practice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.8297316233,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "今日練習したいのは、謎の組織に乗り込んで\n葵さん演じる親友と再会するシーンです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today‚  I want to practice the scene where I infiltrate a mysterious organization\nand reunite with my best friend‚  played by Aoi-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.9870510302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "主人公は、親友がこんな組織にいるはずがない……\nと願っていましたが、思い虚しく再会してしまいます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The heroine believes that her bestie couldn't possibly be\nin such an organization…but her hopes are dashed when they meet again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.1217087395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "親友は組織の中で数々の悪事に手を染めていました\n主人公は打ちひしがれながらも、気丈に振る舞います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Her friend has committed countless evil deeds within the organization.\nWhile devastated‚  the heroine puts on a brave face.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.3999996821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "まずは、私のセリフからいきますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "First‚  I’ll start with my lines.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.8666640599,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（琴乃は今日まで、ずっと勉強と練習を重ねてきた）\n（一体どんな名演技になるのか――）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Kotono has been studying and practicing diligently up until now.）\n（I wonder what kind of amazing performance she’ll deliver――）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.5666622798,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "ほ、本当に、あなた、が～、この組織にいる\nなんて～。どうして……な、の～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-really? You're… in this organization?\nW-why…? H-how…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.4185899098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "でも、もう、受け入れるしかないん、だね～\n分かった、これ以上は聞かにゃい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guess… I just have to accept it‚  huh~?\nOkay‚  I won’t ask any more!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.3636693437,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "わひゃひは、あなたを、止めるー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I‚ I'm‚ going to stop‚ you~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.7303360104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（棒読み、抑揚もめちゃくちゃ、噛みっぱなし……）\n（一体どうなってるんだ！？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Her delivery is stiff‚  her intonation is all over the place‚  and keeps misspelling…）\n（What’s going on!?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.0333289464,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "……こほん\nあの……どうでしたか、私の演技は？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ahem.\nUm… how was my acting?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.5333310445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうだな！\nとりあえず、頑張ってることは伝わったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-well!\nAt least‚  it seemed like you were trying your best.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.9999935786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（参ったな……どこから触れればいいんだ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（This is bad… Where should I even start……）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.9791776139,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "今の{user}さん……私が小学生の時\n学芸会を観に来た両親と同じ顔をしてました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You just now‚  {user}-san… You had the same expression as my parents\nwhen they came to see my elementary school play.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.0393590886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "というと……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you mean…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.7393590886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "両親は気遣いに満ちた笑顔で\nせわしなく目配せをしていたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They were forcing smiles and\nexchanging anxious glances.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.9450053889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "その時、お姉ちゃんも観に来てたんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My older sister came to watch too‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.9116740901,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "「まぁまぁ、琴乃が可愛かったんだからそれでいい\nじゃん」って言ってくれて……ちょっと救われたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and she said‚  “Well‚  Kotono was cute‚  so that's all that matters.”\nThat kind of saved me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.4450074235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "でも、あの頃みたいに甘える訳にはいきません\nどんな厳しいアドバイスも受け止めますから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I can't afford to be spoiled like that anymore.\nI’ll take any advice you have‚  no matter how harsh!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.5783407568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "えぇと、すまない……そうだな、うん\n改善点はあるんだが、どう伝えるといいか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh‚  sorry… Well‚  yeah.\nThere are some areas for improvement‚  but I’m not sure how to put it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.4999956131,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんがこんなに言葉に詰まるなんて……\nよっぽどなんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For {user}-san to be so lost for words…\nIt must be pretty bad.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.2720848527,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "知り合いに、俳優養成所で指導している人がいるから\n相談してみるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know someone who teaches at an acting school.\nI’ll ask them for advice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.654169551,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました……ありがとうございます……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay… Thank you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.1665271798,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫、まだ時間はあるから。……おっと、そろそろ\n番組収録の入り時間だな。行こうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s okay‚  we still have time. …Oh‚  it’s almost\ntime to head to the studio for the show recording. Let's go.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.0333289464,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02-ktn017.m4a",
      "text": "……はい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Okay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.6999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――しばらく経った頃",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Sometime later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.0223127722,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gamecenter-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1366.6595459000064,
          "startTime": 160.3889723181
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1666.6666666999959,
          "startTime": 160.6889794389
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 160.2223127722
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 160.2223127722
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02-ktn018.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、ここで役作りを\nするんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚  are you going to do character research\nhere?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.0889794389,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 165.8223056514
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。バイクのシーンは基本的にCGを使うし\n撮影でもスタントマンの方が乗るんだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. We’re mostly going to use CG for the motorcycle scenes‚\nand a stuntman will be riding the motorcycle during filming…",
